<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <%#*    <hr>%>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: "profile-img" %>
        <div class="skills">
          <h4>Languages used in this application</h4>
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h5><%= skill.title %></h5>
            <h6><%= skill.percent_utilized %>%</h6>
            <div class="progress">
              <div
              class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
              role="progressbar"
              aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
              aria-valuemax="100"
              style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
              ></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>&emsp;I graduated Davis High School in 2003 and enlisted into the US Army where I worked as a Combat Medic/Healthcare Specialist.  During my service, I served in Iraq during Operation Iraqi Freedom 05-06.  I also spent time in Nicaragua providing medical relief for the construction of schools and clinics in the Chinandega province.</p>

        <p>&emsp;After the military, I went through the Utah Peace Officer Standards and Training course and was subsequently hired by Bountiful City Police in Bountiful, Utah.  During my time with Bountiful Police I was a Patrol Officer as well as a PROS II Officer(Elementary School Resource Officer).</p>

        <p>&emsp;I have decided to pusrsue a challenging career in a safer and a less hazardous profession in the Computer Science field.</p>

        <p>&emsp;I am a hard working and driven individual that enjoys new challenges and finding inovative solutions to problems that I may come across.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
            >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
            >
            Education
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#proficient"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="proficient"
            >
            Proficiency
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#knowledge"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="knowledge"
            >
            Knowledge
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              United States Army:
              68W Combat Medic/Healthcare Specialist
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Bountiful City Police:
              Law Enforcement Officer
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Bottega Devcamp: 2018,
              Programming Student
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Weber State University: 2014 - Present,
              BS Computer Science Student
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="proficient">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Ruby
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Rails
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              CSS/SCSS
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              HTML/HTML5
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="knowledge">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Microsoft Office
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Java
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              c++
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Javascript
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jquery
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              PHP
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
